name: Handmade Sterling Silver Pendant on Rolo Chain: Badass Bunny - El Capitan
description:
All Badass Bunny pendants are minimum 18 gauge Sterling Silver.
The chains are 16" Sterling Rolo Chains hand cut and soldered to the Bunny. No two Bunnys will be exactly alike, this too gives exclusivity. All Bunnys are completely hand finished, personally inspected and sold to you almost person to person. 

El Capitan has crossed 9mm pistols. 1 & 6/8" long x 1" wide.
 

Badass Bunny Pendant Weight only averages between: 11 - 13 dwt OR 
17.10g - 20.21g
